Fixed onboarding stuck at 100% issue. Enhanced completeOnboarding() with fallback logic: if setControlRepo fails, directly update config; if config is nil, create minimal config; force @Published update via re-assignment; dispatch objectWillChange on main queue for guaranteed view refresh. Created OnboardingDoneScreenTests.swift with 5 tests for edge cases. Extended OnboardingViewRefreshTests.swift with 2 additional tests. Syntax verified via swift build (successful compilation). Full test execution blocked by pre-existing Preview macro errors.
